0.1.0 xxx, released xxx

Release requirements:
- Supported targets: Kobo and SDL on Linux
- Test on all platforms; update doc/platforms.
- Post kobo binaries.

Features:
- Supported on Kobo Touch and Linux/SDL (may work elsewhere).
- Optional bootloader allows user to select between OcherBook and Kobo's
  native Nickel at startup, for safer end-user testing.
- Parses epub and text.
- Pluggable e-book formats and output devices.
- Browse books by filename.
- Sleep mode.

